# Cursor-First Workflow

- Default to Cursor IDE agent or cloud agent chat for feature inception and implementation.
- Keep CI baseline checks in `.github/workflows/ci.yml` separate from agent automation workflows.
- For automation changes, prefer additive rollout: summarize findings first, then enable write/remediation.
- For visual work, follow `Documentation/style-guide/` and `Documentation/page-guides/`.
